
|WKBCommand: |YKBsemote <feeling>|000

|YKODisplays every supported form of an emote from your perspective. This
includes guild emotes that are currently available to you. Guild emotes from
guilds you do not belong to, or whose abilities are inactive, cannot be
previewed.|000

|WKBExamples:|000
  |YKBsemote grin|000
  |YKBsemote jackin|000

|WKBSee also: |YKBemotes, feelings, guild emotes, emoteapropos|000
